{"tid":177210,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去過歐洲二十個國家旅行 你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-28T16:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T13:29:06.000Z","uid":96063,"like":9,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8635c065c465080d5c516a0a7e8a19214e148de8","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"包括：<br />\n北歐五國<br />\n波羅的海三國<br />\n英國<br />\n愛爾蘭<br />\n法國<br />\n德國<br />\n比利時<br />\n荷蘭<br />\n波蘭<br />\n捷克<br />\n奧地利<br />\n匈牙利<br />\n意大利<br />\n梵蒂岡"},{"pid":"927e18dda19ea7daba0865c90f8dcae2fda9fcd8","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> up返幾張圖啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/012245_7eebe4e4addabde2878573768f3e9e32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F012245_7eebe4e4addabde2878573768f3e9e32.jpg&h=0601e996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/012356_098ffb4d279661aa68eae0866df892e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F012356_098ffb4d279661aa68eae0866df892e5.jpg&h=0e9c1655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/012437_116a9bc64e18135ebe185c328b5fb106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F012437_116a9bc64e18135ebe185c328b5fb106.jpg&h=ef01fd62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/012439_2cd69f4659adab77eac27e09c281604e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F012439_2cd69f4659adab77eac27e09c281604e.jpg&h=76dad7d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63bc5ba4234f4e2a954b1b53fd277f8de5f79cd4","tid":177210,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"最鍾意邊個國家? 點解?"},{"pid":"f685353876242fbde9aab8bc4f7d9e5ef5b3c6c5","tid":177210,"uid":79441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"855f5fa634118e1210af7ac05aeb0472478be267","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最鍾意邊個國家? 點解?</blockquote><br />\n挪威同冰島<br />\n因為呢兩個國家既景真係最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身又好鍾意大自然<br />\n同埋北歐既人都好nice!!!"},{"pid":"529da70862ee2c50e159a79a5c65955063972740","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去咗挪威邊到？</blockquote><br />\nOslo, Bergen(Norway in a nutshell果幾個地方都去左), Stavanger(佈道台同奇蹟石), Lofoten Island, Troms&oslash;, Svalbard"},{"pid":"bbbfd2c1e97469b2a3c60e818bff7cf6907e61d2","tid":177210,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"洗費自己定屋企？<br />\n加埋用左幾錢？<br />\n有咩國家去完好失望？"},{"pid":"3c4a9fea64b0c7188d6333a9ce80231b18794eb6","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗費自己定屋企？<br />\n加埋用左幾錢？<br />\n有咩國家去完好失望？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部分都係自己出<br />\n因為我去果邊exchange<br />\n總共用左8-9萬到<br />\n波羅的海三國（愛沙尼亞、立陶宛、拉脫維亞）<br />\n呢幾個國家又凍又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三日就去哂"},{"pid":"f97865fd50661e20faf88f05e5f8960603c4f63e","tid":177210,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"每個國家玩幾耐先?"},{"pid":"9107549954293d721b35d122c74f2aaacc707bd2","tid":177210,"uid":2435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗費自己定屋企？<br />\n加埋用左幾錢？<br />\n有咩國家去完好失望？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部分都係自己出<br />\n因為我去果邊exchange<br />\n總共用左8-9萬到<br />\n波羅的海三國（愛沙尼亞、立陶宛、拉脫維亞）<br />\n呢幾個國家又凍又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三日就去哂</blockquote><br />\n我黎緊去立陶宛exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無國家推薦必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98a2cfd1aeb250606aae530311948b268dae215","tid":177210,"uid":67729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁<br />\n想知<br />\n深夜係華沙去柏林的火車會係<br />\n櫃台買平定上網買express平<br />\n時間靚仔啲所以就想去櫃台先買<br />\n但一來驚無位二來聽人講波鐵貴<br />\n<br />\n黎緊諗住去幾個月歐洲 呢排搵機票搵車搵到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c7b72bfb74da624ed8fb099dd5849a80733622","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個國家玩幾耐先?</blockquote><br />\n大部分國家都留3-5日<br />\n除左波羅的海 愛爾蘭 梵蒂岡留得1日<br />\n挪威 英國 意大利留得比較耐<br />\n8日以上"},{"pid":"99070327bb9713441f00ad2ad832167f7c041b85","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗費自己定屋企？<br />\n加埋用左幾錢？<br />\n有咩國家去完好失望？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部分都係自己出<br />\n因為我去果邊exchange<br />\n總共用左8-9萬到<br />\n波羅的海三國（愛沙尼亞、立陶宛、拉脫維亞）<br />\n呢幾個國家又凍又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三日就去哂</blockquote><br />\n我黎緊去立陶宛exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無國家推薦必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n立陶宛真係好凍下<br />\n同埋d人好似唔太識英文<br />\n推薦：挪威、冰島、英國、捷克、意大利<br />\n荷蘭可以試下隊草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2badd52b6c0f7803de9e3582030de5e7e64eeee7","tid":177210,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"下半年德國exchange，有冇咩地方介紹<br />\n同想問果邊洗費點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f882d723132c1f525b34859f39f11d9a05804437","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁<br />\n想知<br />\n深夜係華沙去柏林的火車會係<br />\n櫃台買平定上網買express平<br />\n時間靚仔啲所以就想去櫃台先買<br />\n但一來驚無位二來聽人講波鐵貴<br />\n<br />\n黎緊諗住去幾個月歐洲 呢排搵機票搵車搵到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果陣係krakow落柏林<br />\n同埋我係搭通宵巴<br />\n所以唔係好清楚<br />\n但我就建議你試上網買定<br />\n安心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c77beae9cbc6379e648bc567c12d7f3d691bcc9","tid":177210,"uid":82157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"女仔想自己一個去旅行 有無邊幾個國家覺得安全d?"},{"pid":"a9c2e935a9da67a39a6d02ef4f1d5b2cfb121c36","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下半年德國exchange，有冇咩地方介紹<br />\n同想問果邊洗費點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就淨係去左柏林<br />\n但新天鵝堡好似好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39f6ef8f5aed581b443ce01f721e57c583eb85c","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女仔想自己一個去旅行 有無邊幾個國家覺得安全d?</blockquote><br />\n千奇唔好去意大利 好多變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n北歐幾個國家都好安全<br />\n其地我都覺得麻麻 無咩事發生"},{"pid":"d844fe53347459caef2c3e4cb26f706500c6025c","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下半年德國exchange，有冇咩地方介紹<br />\n同想問果邊洗費點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就淨係去左柏林<br />\n但新天鵝堡好似好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗費唔算貴 物價可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e26c0da216074575093bb61a618aeec5f64f79a","tid":177210,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"我計劃緊一轉<br />\n<br />\n巴塞 -&gt; 南法 -&gt; (可能去埋蒙地卡羅) -&gt; 然後內陸機 -&gt; 巴黎 -&gt; 火車上埋 (科隆/布魯塞爾/阿姆斯特丹) 三選二 或 三選三<br />\n<br />\n整個行程可能由 南至北 或 北至南, 主要視乎機票價格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 當中重點係 南法 + 巴塞, 其他地方係配菜, 可以改。<br />\n<br />\n想請問, 我觀察見到, 由香港出發, 較平機票應該係由 阿姆斯特丹入? (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n因為open jaw, 想請教邊到入 + 邊到出最抵玩?<br />\n或者有咩建議?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081de4463bba009d78e28ee6359e1403d15e01ee","tid":177210,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"下次去歐洲想去西班牙，德國，荷蘭，克羅地亞，想問下點排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分開兩次都得，因為上次英法意，有d想去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cd0c57a44801d23e45b02d4ed821914c29fdb7","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我計劃緊一轉<br />\n<br />\n巴塞 -&gt; 南法 -&gt; (可能去埋蒙地卡羅) -&gt; 然後內陸機 -&gt; 巴黎 -&gt; 火車上埋 (科隆/布魯塞爾/阿姆斯特丹) 三選二 或 三選三<br />\n<br />\n整個行程可能由 南至北 或 北至南, 主要視乎機票價格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 當中重點係 南法 + 巴塞, 其他地方係配菜, 可以改。<br />\n<br />\n想請問, 我觀察見到, 由香港出發, 較平機票應該係由 阿姆斯特丹入? (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n因為open jaw, 想請教邊到入 + 邊到出最抵玩?<br />\n或者有咩建議?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無去巴塞同南法 但如果你話阿姆斯特丹平d就果到入 我諗巴塞出都應該平dd？好似會多d機"},{"pid":"a21c632b88169ebaa7c12a6a5c59ec23d4f8b191","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次去歐洲想去西班牙，德國，荷蘭，克羅地亞，想問下點排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分開兩次都得，因為上次英法意，有d想去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國你會去邊先<br />\n但我諗西班牙 德國 同荷蘭一次<br />\n克羅地亞 另一次 玩埋奧地利 匈牙利 果邊好似抵d"},{"pid":"1622e75d46353f4c0c972ff074912c47363809e0","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"好狗 我咁認真答 係咁負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5f534dea2aec789cdaf7166b0799b3e01a2b2b","tid":177210,"uid":18416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"有冇咩特別野發生？ 俾人偷野之類"},{"pid":"3caabc9b7dbdde45da61635051fd4aceb114a169","tid":177210,"uid":96063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咩特別野發生？ 俾人偷野之類</blockquote><br />\n比人偷野就無 但意大利好多麻甩佬會目及你對腳 仲試過握握下手比人用手指撩我掌心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1863d0da5207790e70089cf8ea00d206cb6cfbb4","tid":177210,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗費自己定屋企？<br />\n加埋用左幾錢？<br />\n有咩國家去完好失望？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部分都係自己出<br />\n因為我去果邊exchange<br />\n總共用左8-9萬到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">波羅的海三國（愛沙尼亞、立陶宛、拉脫維亞）</span><br />\n呢幾個國家又凍又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三日就去哂</blockquote><br />\n我打算下個月去, 真係好悶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7b5650c73cf6118c0cb1e6a9b11bbfc0139814","tid":177210,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁<br />\n想知<br />\n深夜係華沙去柏林的火車會係<br />\n櫃台買平定上網買expres